@node Extend
@toc Main

EXTEND XSNOW

Well, I really would like to see a _nice_ snow blanker
module. xsnow is just a first step. But I'm not good at
drawing nice snowmen, trees etc. so it may look a bit
"childish". If You have any idea (snowflakes falling on
the WB screen like in xsnow, nicer landscapes, santa's
sled like in xsnow) feel free to change xsnow and to
submit it to aminet.

